Document: ColorPicker
Path: godot/classes/class_colorpicker.rst
Summary: Describes the ColorPicker widget, its purpose, and how it differs from ColorPickerButton.

A widget that provides an interface for selecting or modifying a color. It can optionally provide functionalities like a color sampler (eyedropper), color modes, and presets.

Note: This control is the color picker widget itself. You can use a ColorPickerButton instead if you need a button that brings up a ColorPicker in a popup.
