Document: ColorPicker
Path: godot/classes/class_colorpicker.rst
Summary: This section describes the properties available for configuring a ColorPicker node, including visibility of UI elements, color selection behavior, and color representation.

Property Descriptions:

can_add_swatches (bool): If true, it's possible to add presets under Swatches. If false, the button to add presets is disabled. Default: true.
Method: set_can_add_swatches(value: bool)
Method: are_swatches_enabled()

color (Color): The currently selected color. Default: Color(1, 1, 1, 1).
Method: set_pick_color(value: Color)
Method: get_pick_color()

color_mode (ColorModeType): The currently selected color mode. Default: 0.
Method: set_color_mode(value: ColorModeType)
Method: get_color_mode()

color_modes_visible (bool): If true, the color mode buttons are visible. Default: true.
Method: set_modes_visible(value: bool)
Method: are_modes_visible()

deferred_mode (bool): If true, the color will apply only after the user releases the mouse button, otherwise it will apply immediately even in mouse motion event (which can cause performance issues). Default: false.
Method: set_deferred_mode(value: bool)
Method: is_deferred_mode()

edit_alpha (bool): If true, shows an alpha channel slider (opacity). Default: true.
Method: set_edit_alpha(value: bool)
Method: is_editing_alpha()

edit_intensity (bool): If true, shows an intensity slider. The intensity is applied as follows: convert the color to linear encoding, multiply it by 2 ** intensity, and then convert it back to nonlinear sRGB encoding. Default: true.
Method: set_edit_intensity(value: bool)
Method: is_editing_intensity()

hex_visible (bool): If true, the hex color code input field is visible. Default: true.
Method: set_hex_visible(value: bool)
Method: is_hex_visible()

picker_shape (PickerShapeType): The shape of the color space view. Default: 0.
Method: set_picker_shape(value: PickerShapeType)
Method: get_picker_shape()

presets_visible (bool): If true, the Swatches and Recent Colors presets are visible. Default: true.
Method: set_presets_visible(value: bool)
Method: are_presets_visible()

sampler_visible (bool): If true, the color sampler and color preview are visible. Default: true.
Method: set_sampler_visible(value: bool)
Method: is_sampler_visible()

sliders_visible (bool): If true, the color sliders are visible. Default: true.
Method: set_sliders_visible(value: bool)
Method: are_sliders_visible()
